::Iron Raptor::

Iron Raptor frowns and nods. She would have to watch these four. They've allready abandoned the Maximals once.

"Well, everyone deserves a second chance. We're training right now. Here, I'll show you to the holo-rooms."

She walks off, her scanners locating the other Maximals, and her following them. IR looks back to make sure the new Maximals were following behind.
